title: Tropical Banana Cupcakes
ingredients: ['250g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '110g butter', '220g dark brown soft sugar', '2 large eggs', '3 medium bananas', '1 tablespoon rum extract', '100g desiccated coconut', '60g chopped dried pineapple']
